{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add log filter input\n\nAdd real-time filtering controls for live logs in the VM detail view:\n- filterText: case-insensitive text search within displayed logs\n- filterStream: dropdown to filter by stream (all, stdout, stderr)\n- filteredLogs getter: computed property combining both filters\n\nThe filter applies only to Live mode logs (in-memory filtering), not\nthe historical Search mode which queries the server.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
